---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="450m² Garden & 8m Pool — Your Private Outdoor Retreat | Casa dos Duques"
  description="Explore the beautiful 450m² garden and 8m pool at Casa dos Duques. Several lounge areas, barbecue terrace, and stunning views — your private outdoor paradise in Abiul."
  canonical="/garden/"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6">450 m² of Garden & Pool — Your Private Outdoor Retreat</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
      <img src="/images/garden-1.jpg" alt="Garden view" class="rounded-lg h-64 w-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
      <img src="/images/garden-2.jpg" alt="Pool area" class="rounded-lg h-64 w-full object-cover" loading="eager" />
    </div>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">🏊 The Pool</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Our 8-meter swimming pool is the heart of the garden on warm summer days. Set within the 
        450m² grounds, it offers a refreshing escape with plenty of space to lounge, read, and soak 
        up the Portuguese sun.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-3">
        ⚠️ Safety note: The pool does not have a gate or lock. Children must be supervised at all times.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">🌳 The Garden</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed mb-3">
        The garden is one of Casa dos Duques's greatest assets. With 450 square metres of space, 
        there are several distinct lounge areas where guests can relax in privacy, sunbathe in comfort, 
        play games, or simply enjoy the tranquillity of the countryside.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed">
        The garden offers views of the surrounding valley and mountains, creating a peaceful backdrop 
        for your holiday.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-olive-700 mb-4">🍖 Terrace & BBQ</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-warm leading-relaxed">
        The outdoor terrace is equipped with a barbecue, perfect for evening meals al fresco. 
        Share a meal, watch the sunset, and enjoy the company of your loved ones in this 
        beautiful setting.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <CTASection
    title="Experience the Garden"
    subtitle="Book your stay and enjoy your private outdoor paradise"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Check Availability', href: '/booking/' }}
    variant="olive"
  />
</BaseLayout>
